    CR -->|Creative synthesis| B[GPT-4]
    CR -->|Mathematical analysis| C[Gemini]
    CR -->|Code generation| D[Best available]
    CR -->|Cost-sensitive| E[Ollama local]
    A --> U[Uniform Output]
    B --> U
    C --> U
    D --> U
    E --> U`}
		/>

